Output docs/src/assets/terminal/density.gif
Set Width 1200
Set Height 620
Set FontSize 14
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.5

Sleep 500ms
Type "./target/release/kuva density examples/data/samples.tsv --value expression --color-by group --filled --title Density --x-label Expression --y-label Density --terminal --term-width 108 --term-height 32"
Sleep 3s
Enter
Sleep 10s
